==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Strait
<hw>Strait</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <amorph>[<pos>Compar.</pos>
<adjf>Straiter</adjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>superl.</pos>
<adjf>Straitest</adjf>.]</amorph> <ety>[OE. <ets>straight</ets>,
<ets>streyt</ets>, <ets>streit</ets>, OF. <ets>estreit</ets>,
<ets>estroit</ets>, F. <ets>⟦eacute⟧troit</ets>, from L.
<ets>strictus</ets> drawn together, close, tight, p. p. of
<ets>stringere</ets> to draw tight. See 2nd <er>Strait</er>, and cf.
<er>Strict</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Narrow; not broad.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Strait</qex> is the gate, and narrow is the way, which
leadeth unto life, and few there be that find it.</q> <rj><qau>Matt.
vii. 14.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Too <qex>strait</qex> and low our cottage doors.</q>
<rj><qau>Emerson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Tight; close; closely fitting.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Close; intimate; near; familiar.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧A <xex>strait</xex> degree of favor.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Sir P. Sidney.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>4.</sn> <def>Strict; scrupulous; rigorous.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Some certain edicts and some <qex>strait</qex> decrees.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>straitest</qex> sect of our religion.</q> <rj><qau>Acts
xxvi. 5 (Rev. Ver.).</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>5.</sn> <def>Difficult; distressful; straited.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To make your <qex>strait</qex> circumstances yet
<qex>straiter</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Secker.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>6.</sn> <def>Parsimonious; niggargly; mean.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I beg cold comfort, and you are so <qex>strait</qex>,⟦br⟧
And so ingrateful, you deny me that.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Strait</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Strait
<hw>Strait</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Strictly;
