HEADWORD: Strait
<hw>Strait</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To put to difficulties.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Straiten</ent>⟦br⟧
